'''Bandos armour''' is a set of [[armour]] for [[members]] that requires 65 [[Defence]] to wear. It is dropped by [[General Graardor]] and his bodyguards in the [[God Wars Dungeon]].

Its defence bonuses are between [[Dragon armour|dragon]] and [[3rd age melee equipment|3rd age]], and is also the second best armour to give strength bonuses, behind the [[Torva armour]] (except for the boots, which do not provide any strength bonus), along with [[Inquisitor's armour]], which provides more benefits for crush weaponry but penalises slash and stab attack styles.

